## ClientApp (React admin SPA, nested under WebApp - the only project that serves a website;
## RssService/ApiService are headless) - Vite build output lands in WebApp's own wwwroot (see
## ClientApp/vite.config.ts), so wwwroot is generated, not source, same as bin/obj.
## (Already-tracked wwwroot files from before this rule covered this path stay tracked
## regardless - this only affects new/untracked ones.)
src/WebApp/wwwroot/
src/WebApp/ClientApp/node_modules/

